  "content": "\u003cp\u003eTired of the limitations of REST APIs?\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThis article explores modern alternatives like GraphQL, gRPC, and WebSockets that can unlock a world of possibilities beyond REST for your web applications.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eREST has served us well, but it\u0026#39;s time to move on.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eLearn about:\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eâ€¢ The limitations of forcing real-world entities into rigid REST structures\u003cbr /\u003eâ€¢ Why versioning in REST can be a nightmare for developers\u003cbr /\u003eâ€¢ How inefficient JSON can be for data transfer\u003cbr /\u003eâ€¢ Why OpenAPI specs aren\u0026#39;t a silver bullet\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eDiscover exciting new API design options:\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eâ€¢ GraphQL: The \u0026quot;Choose Your Own Adventure\u0026quot; API for flexible data fetching\u003cbr /\u003eâ€¢ gRPC: The \u0026quot;Cut the Drama\u0026quot; API for clear and efficient communication\u003cbr /\u003eâ€¢ WebSockets: The go-to solution for real-time data updates\u003cbr /\u003eâ€¢ Server-Sent Events (SSE): Simple server-to-client updates for live scores or notifications\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe API landscape is ever-evolving. Don\u0026#39;t be afraid to break free from REST and explore new possibilities!\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eSee the full post here: \u003ca href=\"https://sudorandom.dev/posts/restless/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" translate=\"no\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"invisible\"\u003ehttps://\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"\"\u003esudorandom.dev/posts/restless/\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"invisible\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eDid I miss any good alternatives?\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://infosec.exchange/tags/webdev\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"tag\"\u003e#\u003cspan\u003ewebdev\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e \u003ca href=\"https://infosec.exchange/tags/api\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"tag\"\u003e#\u003cspan\u003eapi\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e \u003ca href=\"https://infosec.exchange/tags/graphql\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"tag\"\u003e#\u003cspan\u003egraphql\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e \u003ca href=\"https://infosec.exchange/tags/grpc\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"tag\"\u003e#\u003cspan\u003egrpc\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e hashtag \u003ca href=\"https://infosec.exchange/tags/websockets\" class=\"mention hashtag\" rel=\"tag\"\u003e#\u003cspan\u003ewebsockets\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e",
